column1: ZIGZAG1
posix_time: time in seconds since the 1970 epoch.
x_mocap: x position in m from the ASTA mocap frame.
y_mocap: y position in m from the ASTA mocap frame.
z_mocap: z position in m from the ASTA mocap frame.
qx_mocap: quaternion i component from the ASTA mocap frame.
qy_mocap: quaternion j component from the ASTA mocap frame.
qz_mocap: quaternion k component from the ASTA mocap frame.
qw_mocap: quaternion scalar component from the ASTA mocap frame.
ax: x dir body-fixed acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
ay: y dir body-fixed acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
az: z dir body-fixed acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
wx: angular velocity in rad/s around body-fixed x axis measured by IMU.
wy: angular velocity in rad/s around body-fixed y axis measured by IMU.
wz: angular velocity in rad/s around body-fixed z axis measured by IMU.
ax_c: x dir gravity compensated acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
ay_c: y dir gravity compensated acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
az_c: z dir gravity compensated acceleration in m/s/s measured by IMU.
qx: quaternion i component from the NED frame to body fixed frame measured by IMU.
qy: quaternion j component from the NED frame to body fixed frame measured by IMU.
qz: quaternion k component from the NED frame to body fixed frame measured by IMU.
qw: quaternion scalar component from the NED frame to body fixed frame measured by IMU.
pwm0: Motor pulse width modulation for motor0 in microseconds.
pwm1: Motor pulse width modulation for motor1 in microseconds.
pwm2: Motor pulse width modulation for motor2 in microseconds.
pwm3: Motor pulse width modulation for motor3 in microseconds.
pwm4: Motor pulse width modulation for motor4 in microseconds.
pwm5: Motor pulse width modulation for motor5 in microseconds.
N0: Motor thrust in N for motor0.
N1: Motor thrust in N for motor1.
N2: Motor thrust in N for motor2.
N3: Motor thrust in N for motor3.
N4: Motor thrust in N for motor4.
N5: Motor thrust in N for motor5.
Fx: Body fixed surge force (N).
Fy: Body fixed sway force (N).
Fz: Body fixed heart force (N).
Mx: Body fixed roll moment (Nm).
My: Body fixed pitch moment (Nm).
Mz: Body fixed yaw moment (Nm).
